      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="image1.jpg"/>
            <!--filenames for photos associated with this letter. Example: <pb n="1" facs="image1.jpg image2.jpg image3.jpg"/> -->
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <name type="place" ref="Edgeworthtown"/>
                  <date when="1816-08-04"/>January 24, 1834. </dateline>
               <salute>
                  Sir
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
               <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_1834-01_page01.jpg"/>
               Sir<lb/>
               I approve of the title page<lb/>
               for <title ref="./Workography.xml#Pract1">Helen</title><lb/></p>
               <p>I beg you will send the<lb/>
               first copy you can have<lb/>
               stitched together to<lb/>
               <placeName ref=".Placeography.xml#1-North-Audley-Street_ENK"><choice><orig>N<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>.</orig><reg>Number</reg></choice> 1 North Audley Street</placeName><lb/>
               to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Lestock Wilson</persName><lb/></p>
               <p>Also I request that instead<lb/>
               of 9 copies as ordered in<lb/>
               my last to be sent to<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. L Wilson</persName> you will<lb/>
               send her <hi rend="underline">ten</hi> - independent<lb/>
               of that stitched copy mentioned<lb/>
               above<lb/></p>
               <p>I am anxious that you<lb/>
               should send the <hi rend="underline">revises</hi> of<lb/>
               the last sheets to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. L Wilson</persName><lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
               I am Sir<lb/>
               Your <choice><orig>Obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</orig><reg>Obedient</reg></choice> <choice><orig>Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</orig><reg>Servant</reg></choice><lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName><lb/>
            </closer>
            
            <pb n="4" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_1834-01_page02.jpg"/>
            
            <closer>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>R Bentley Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi><lb/></addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
